唔想開post<br />\n唔想接觸個世界<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n要搭出第一步，試下識下其他人，你要自己諗下，如果成日咁諗傷心事，對自己冇幫助，我之前都係咁，我好負能量，但我唔可以咁落去，自己唔開心，自己辛苦姐，同多啲朋友傾訴，解開心結，如果搵唔到，搵我都得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"057ff2119b5e1b21f763028c5eec8c4afacf77cc","tid":134903,"uid":24948,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-26T01:24:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>試吓搵下自己長處<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n長處啊我都唔知呀<br />\n成世人淨係識得走聰明捷徑<br />\n好似都冇用心做嗰件事咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n巴打我試過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n如果以我情況咁 我因為無所事事 做咩都無心情咁 試下搵d野比自己做 慢慢搵到方向<br />\n加油<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5326582201e80d28f283b4130b2bdaa954aa8557","tid":134903,"uid":41859,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-26T01:25:59.000Z","msg":"原來同你一樣"},{"pid":"ee4d77165a8144dec2daba04e7e3f6831e031559","tid":134903,"uid":37005,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-26T01:39:40.000Z","msg":"你需要一個情人幫你重拾熱情"},{"pid":"d590ffe7a6949c6236ef88856e8a72ef0256487e","tid":134903,"uid":22488,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-26T01:40:51.000Z","msg":"去做一樣運動 做到咩都唔記得哂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0aa6001936dee85f40c7194cd4e56b6d105ba30b","tid":134903,"uid":50157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-26T01:42:00.000Z","msg":"Same here<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不過未到厭世咁嚴重 只係乜都唔願理"},{"pid":"b746ad9cdf9a01442fec16e91bc362734dd37314","tid":134903